cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.RO 

This paper is primarily focused on computer vision, specifically on optical flow estimation. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also extensively uses deep learning techniques, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the paper deals with video processing, which could place it in cs.MM (Multimedia) and cs.RO (Robotics).
